\id GLO - Kuman NT [kue] -Papua New Guinea 2008 (DBL 2014) 
\h Kuman Baibel mina ka tau bounga i mambuno yegl 
\toc2 Kuman Baibel mina ka tau bounga i mambuno yegl 
\toc1 Kuman Baibel mina ka tau bounga i mambuno yegl 
\mt2 Kuman Baibel mina ka tau bounga i mambuno yegl  
\li1 \k Anka\k* — Taragl yumbun dongwa sip atnekra kanekogl mundi nigl atne endigo ana sip akegi dungo nigle bolamugl pangwa.  
\li1 \k Aposel\k* — Yesus kongun dendungo ere endeingwa yomba.  
\li1 \k Baklain\k* — Kan kande bai akingwa towiye moglkwa.  
\li1 \k Baptais\k* — Yesus wedi pirngi dindre ana bitno nigl biglkwa mo nigl paingwa.  
\li1 \k Basket\k* — Dengigl gagl.  
\li1 \k Bis\k* — Taragl memgo kembra kembra wigl ende nunguno mina tengingwa.  
\li1 \k Biukul\k* — Bu bendingwa taragl.  
\li1 \k Blesing\k* — Yomba nomano ya nangino pre God taragl wakai kane kane ere akepledi tongwa.  
\li1 \k Boma nuglo\k* — Endi nuglo kama sidangingwa.  
\li1 \k Bot\k* — Arnga kande nigle bolamugl wu ikine ikine engwa.  
\li1 \k Buk\k* — Muno beglkwa yaundo merkinde pangwa.  
\li1 \k Bugla-kamel\k* — Bugla-kau mereyegl moko mina sunguno begine orkwa.  
\li1 \k Diglimbi\k* — Pepa yaundo olto ake perikwa.  
\li1 \k Disaipel\k* — Yesus aglendi yungwa ya mokomugl eingwa yomba.  
\li1 \k Fis\k* — Buglo bagle.  
\li1 \k Gavana\k* — Provins mina yagl kande mogl ende okuna ongwa.  
\li1 \k God, god kimbi\k* — Neno Kande God pre ka gumamugl “G” kande pangwa. Ana god kimbi pre “g” kembra pangwa.  
\li1 \k God kingdomo\k* — Heven suna taragl prapra meglkwa ya yomba prapra God mina atnekra mounga.  
\li1 \k Gon\k* — Di kumba prak nekrumara.  
\li1 \k Heven\k* — Kamun mitna i yene God dumomo.  
\li1 \k Hibru\k* — Juda yomba kangino ta ya te ye kanno.  
\li1 \k Holi\k* — Yomba du-yene ya aglau ta paikrukwa. Ana taragl ta mundu moglkwa mo yongwa God ongumuglo mina deglimbi yeikrukwa.  
\li1 \k Holi Spirit\k* — God Murumbuglomo, Murumbuglo Wakai, Mundu Murumbuglo.  
\li1 \k Kamda\k* — Yungu wakai kengwa yagle.  
\li1 \k Kantri\k* — Kamun kande Austrelia mereyegl.  
\li1 \k Kaunsol\k* — Juda yomba kande kamambuno ende okna pindre ka digi dingwa yomba.  
\li1 \k Kingdom\k* — King kamunmo mina taragl kanekane meglkwa ya yomba prapra ye mina atnekra meglkwa.  
\li1 \k Kot\k* — Aglau erikwa ka tange akedu endingwa.  
\li1 \k Kristen\k* — Yesus wedi pirngidi baptais erikwa yomba.  
\li1 \k Kum endungwa\k* — Okuna no yegl ere-ere onga, nombo gogl ya kama nuglono usuwara embrika, ake kum endungo i kokun gagl mina engrikwa. Pisin ka mina kum endungwa i kangiye “purpel” wendumga.  
\li1 \k Lo\k* — Binga ka ya te ka kindine.  
\li1 \k Lotu\k* — Kristen wagle makaisi God dembiye karaugl ereteingwa.  
\li1 \k Mastet mongo\k* — Kiglawa mongo kembra mo endi poglko mongo kembra mereyegl.  
\li1 \k Ofa\k* — God Wam yomba pre tongo ana yomba taragl kanekane God pre teingwa.  
\li1 \k Okupo\k* — Kombuglo kembra kinde merkinde. Pisin ka mina nono waisan wedumga.  
\li1 \k Pasova\k* — God kuko yei Israel yomba akepledi ere yongwa, ipre ye gunyei kaiya mokna ere neingwa.  
\li1 \k Pentikos\k* — Holi Spirit ende atne ungwa engemo.  
\li1 \k Pepa\k* — Muno beglkwa yaundo suwara, te muno beglkwa yaundo merkinde pangwa.  
\li1 \k Pretorim\k* — Gavman yunguno kande mina kula ta katange tange di pra di-di erimara.  
\li1 \k Pris\k* — Kamambuno kongun orkwa yagle, Juda yomba ofano kombuglange gagl God te-te orkwa yagle.  
\li1 \k Propet\k* — God ka ditongo pirtre ana ye di yomba teingwa mongomo pai yungwa.  
\li1 \k Provins\k* — Dumo kande ta Rom makanmo ikine sugl moglkwa.  
\li1 \k Rabai\k* — Hibru kanno mina ka beke tongwa yagle.  
\li1 \k Sabat\k* — Moglpirkwa enge i ande enge 6 kongun ertre ana ande enge 7 mina moglpirkwa. Juda yomba ye God lomo ditomere ere ana Sarere wakan mogl God dembiye sitengwa.  
\li1 \k Sanda\k* — Kungo demine orkwa.  
\li1 \k Sawol\k* — Ikan.  
\li1 \k Silva\k* — Ain kaneta pesungwa moni mongo bekingwa.  
\li1 \k Sios\k* — Yesus wedi pirngi dingwa yomba yungu ombuno.  
\li1 \k Siti\k* — Dumo kande yungu togl yei winambo dungwa.  
\li1 \k Spirit\k* — Murumbuglo yomba mina moglkwa.  
\li1 \k Spirit kinde\k* — Murumbuglo kinde, gigl kinde, gigl kumo kangiye.  
\li1 \k Takis\k* — Yomba monino gavman teingwa.  
\li1 \k Tisa\k* — Ka beke tongwa yagle.  
\li1 \k Wit\k* — Kugl ta pango mongo dikir mereyegl. Ye si dendi wagle ere plawa bekingwa.  
\li1 \k Yaglkande, yagl kande\k* — God ya Yesus pre ka gumamugl “Y” kande pangwa. Ana yomba kande pre “y” kembra pangwa.  
\b  
\p Yomba ya angai dumo kangino tau i Tok Pisin nunguno embriye pamere Kuman ka mina bounga.  